title: 1925–26 Dundee United F.C. season
text:
The 1925–26 season was the 15th year of <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> played by <a href="Dundee%20United%20F.C.">Dundee United</a>, and covers the period from 1 July 1925 to 30 June 1926.
Match results.
Dundee United played a total of 41 matches during the 1925–26 season.
Legend.
All results are written with Dundee United's score first.
Own goals in italics
